r hard-coded rules. A quality-inspection system detecting novel defect types without retraining, a robotic arm grasping unfamiliar objects, or a financial model adapting to new fraud patterns all require AI."}],"\n",["$","p","p-3",{"children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Market scale (2026)"}],":"]}],"\n",["$","ul","ul-1",{"children":["\n",["$","li","li-0",{"children":["Global AI in manufacturing: ",["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"$$21.6B"}]," (2026), CAGR 36% [MarketsandMarkets, 2025]"]}],"\n",["$","li","li-1",{"children":["Intelligent automation market: ",["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"$$19.8B"}]," (2025), projected $65.7B by 2030 [IDC, 2025]"]}],"\n",["$","li","li-2",{"children":["Enterprise AI for operational automation: ",["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"68%"}]," of Fortune 500 [Gartner, 2026]"]}],"\n"]}],"\n",["$","hr","hr-2",{}],"\n",["$","h2","h2-2",{"children":"2. Traditional vs. AI-Driven Automation"}],"\n",["$","table","table-0",{"children":[["$","thead","thead-0",{"children":["$","tr","tr-0",{"children":[["$","th","th-0",{"children":"Dimension"}],["$","th","th-1",{"children":"Traditional (Rule-Based)"}],["$","th","th-2",{"children":"AI-Driven"}]]}]}],["$","tbody","tbody-0",{"children":[["$","tr","tr-0",{"children":[["$","td","td-0",{"children":["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Logic source"}]}],["$","td","td-1",{"children":"Human-programmed rules"}],["$","td","td-2",{"children":"Learned from data"}]]}],["$","tr","tr-1",{"children":[["$","td","td-0",{"children":["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Handles variability"}]}],["$","td","td-1",{"children":"No — fails on exceptions"}],["$","td","td-2",{"children":"Yes — generalizes within distribution"}]]}],["$","tr","tr-2",{"children":[["$","td","td-0",{"children":["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Maintenance"}]}],["$","td","td-1",{"children":"Update rules manually"}],["$","td","td-2",{"children":"Retrain on new data"}]]}],["$","tr","tr-3",{"children":[["$","td","td-0",{"ch