30:["$","ul","ul-2",{"children":["\n",["$","li","li-0",{"children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Predictive maintenance"}],": ML models on vibration, temperature, and current sensors predict failures 2–6 weeks ahead. Siemens, GE, and SKF deploy these systems. Reported outcome: 30–50% reduction in unplanned downtime [McKinsey, 2023]."]}],"\n",["$","li","li-1",{"children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Quality control"}],": CNN-based vision achieves >99% defect detection accuracy on production lines (vs. 92–96% for human inspectors). Foxconn reported 30% defect reduction post-deployment."]}],"\n",["$","li","li-2",{"children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Demand forecasting"}],": Amazon's gradient boosting + LSTM models achieve <10% MAPE on weekly demand per SKU."]}],"\n"]}]
