35:["$","ul","ul-4",{"children":["\n",["$","li","li-0",{"children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"YOLOv11 (2024)"}],": 54.9% mAP on COCO at real-time speeds [Ultralytics, 2024]. Standard for industrial inspection."]}],"\n",["$","li","li-1",{"children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Segment Anything Model (SAM 2, 2024)"}],": Meta's zero-shot segmentation model; handles images and video without task-specific training."]}],"\n",["$","li","li-2",{"children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Grounding DINO + SAM"}],": Open-vocabulary detection pipeline—detects any object class from a text prompt. Enables flexible bin-picking robots without pre-programmed object libraries."]}],"\n"]}]
